sentences.en: The Palace of Westminster, also known as the Houses of Parliament or Westminster Palace, is the meeting place of the two houses of the Parliament of the United Kingdom.

sentences.en: We now have the pleasure of confirming that your bankers the Westminster Bank Ltd, have accepted our Draft for 6 000 USD payable within thirty days of sight.

sentences.en: In March, extremist Khalid Masood ploughed into pedestrians along Westminster Bridge before stabbing PC Keith Palmer to death outside the Houses of Parliament.

sentences.en: To an outsider, Britain usually evokes images such as the Queen, the Houses of Parliament, Westminster Abbey, the Tower of London and the southern counties of England.
